Package: Numerico
Type: Package
Title: Numerical methods 
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Matias Rosenstein
Maintainer: matias.rosenstein00@gmail.com
Description: Provides implementations of common numerical methods in R, including interpolation (Newton, Lagrange, Hermite), equation solving methods (Newton-Raphson, bisection, regula falsi), difference calculations, Taylor polynomials, splines, Bernoulli numbers, and more.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
